extends ../layouts/master.pug

include  ../components/navigation
include ../components/reviews-card
include ../components/guides-card
include ../components/slider-buttons
include ../components/modals

block content 
  .about-page.main-page
    section.section.section--first(data-aos='fade-up')
      .container
        +navigation(page="About")
    section.section.section--md.section--visible
      .about-page__hero(data-aos='fade-up')
        .about-page__hero-container
          img.about-page__hero-img(src="assets/images/about-hero.jpg", alt="")
          img.about-page__hero-img--mobile(src="assets/images/about-hero-mobile.jpg", alt="")
        .about-page__hero-content
          .about-page__hero-title 
            |Best Guides
          .about-page__hero-label 
            |Saint Petersburg
    section.section.section--xl 
      .container
        .about-page__section 
          .about-page__section-container(data-aos='fade-up') 
            p.about-page__section-text 
              |Back in 2010, several St. Petersburg guides, graduates of St. Petersburg University, joined together, created their own website and started working together. We saw no obstacles and were ready to move mountains. And&nbsp;most importantly, we loved our city and our profession very much.
          .about-page__section-title(data-aos='fade-up') 
            |This is how the Best Guides company appeared.
    section.section 
      .container
        .about-page__row 
          .about-page__col(data-aos='fade-up')
            .about-page__caption 
              |We grew and developed very quickly. After 2 years, we have already started conducting excursions in Moscow, then in Novgorod. And a couple of years later we had wonderful guides in Tallinn, then in Berlin, in Stockholm, in Helsinki and, finally, in Copenhagen.
          .about-page__col(data-aos='fade-up')
            p.about-page__text 
              |Time passed. A new generation of guides has arrived. Then-another one. But the selection criteria have remained the same â€“ young, energetic, talented people who are in love with their city and their profession come to us.
    section.section   
      .container 
        .about-page__team 
          .about-page__team-container(data-aos='fade-up')  
            .about-page__team-frame
              img.about-page__team-img(src="assets/images/about-team.jpg", alt="")
            .about-page__team-label
              |Best Guides
          section.section.section--xxl
            .about-page__team-row 
              .about-page__team-col(data-aos='fade-up')
                p.about-page__text 
                  |We are sure that the profession of a guide is not just one of the most interesting professions in the world, but also one of the most important. Guides are the face of the city. They meet guests, they tell about the city, they bring knowledge. It depends on the guide how interesting, meaningful, and informative your trip will be.
              .about-page__team-col(data-aos='fade-up')
                p.about-page__text 
                  |We have our own criterion for a good excursion. If after the tour our guests say: "How interesting! I had no idea! I will definitely read more about it, what exactly can I read? " - so the tour was a success.
          section.section 
            h2.about-page__title(data-aos='fade-up')  
              |We are proud of our guides and we are sure that they are the best!
    section.section 
      .container 
        .main-page__top
          .main-page__top-row(data-aos='fade-up')
            .main-page__top-col
              +slider-buttons(next = 3 prev = 4)
            .main-page__top-col
              .main-page__title 
                |Team
            .main-page__top-col
              +button(tag = 'a' href = '#')
                |Read more
        .team(data-aos='fade-up')
          .swiper-container.swiper-container--slide-width-auto.swiper-container--slide-height-max.swiper-container--visible(data-slider-id='1' data-slider-next='3' data-slider-prev='4')
            .swiper-wrapper 
              each item in data.team
                .swiper-slide 
                  .team__item
                    +guides-card(sign = item.sign name = item.name src = item.src)
    section.section 
      .container 
        .main-page__top(data-aos='fade-up')
          .main-page__top-row 
            .main-page__top-col
              +slider-buttons(next = 5 prev = 6)
            .main-page__top-col
              .main-page__title 
                |Reviews about us
            .main-page__top-col.main-page__mobile
              +button(tag = 'a' href = '#' target='_blank')
                |All reviews on Tripadviser
        .swiper-container.swiper-container--visible.swiper-container--visible--mobile.swiper-container--slide-width-auto.swiper-container--slide-height-max(data-slider-id='1' data-slider-next='5' data-slider-prev='6' data-aos='fade-up')
          .swiper-wrapper
            each item in data.mainReviews
              .swiper-slide
                +reviews-card(name = item.name)
        .about-page__button(data-aos='fade-up') 
          +button(tag = 'a' href = '#' target='_blank')
            |All reviews on Tripadviser
    section.section 
      .container 
        .main-page__standarts 
          .rail
          .main-page__standarts-inner 
            .main-page__standarts-wrapper(data-aos='fade-up')
              .main-page__title 
                |We observe sanitary and hygienic standards
            .main-page__standarts-row
              .main-page__standarts-col(data-aos='fade-up')
                .main-page__standarts-img
                  +standarts-1-svg
                .main-page__standarts-text  
                  |All the equipment we used is disinfected before each trip
              .main-page__standarts-col(data-aos='fade-up')
                .main-page__standarts-img
                  +standarts-2-svg
                .main-page__standarts-text  
                  |We provide individual protection for each person on our tours
              .main-page__standarts-col(data-aos='fade-up')
                .main-page__standarts-img
                  +standarts-3-svg
                .main-page__standarts-text  
                  |Antiseptics are available on all tours
              .main-page__standarts-col(data-aos='fade-up')
                .main-page__standarts-img
                  +standarts-4-svg
                .main-page__standarts-text  
                  |Personal headphones are disinfected after each tour
          .rail.rail--reverse
    section.section 
      .container 
        .main-page__features
          .main-page__features-container 
            .main-page__features-row 
              each item in data.mainFeatures
                .main-page__features-col(data-aos='fade-up')
                  .main-page__features-img 
                    img.main-page__features-icon(src="assets/images/svg/" + item.src, alt="")
                  .main-page__features-text 
                    |#{item.text}
              .main-page__properties
                .main-page__properties-container 
                  .main-page__properties-row 
                    .main-page__properties-col(data-aos='fade-up') 
                      .main-page__properties-img 
                        +properties-1-svg
                      .main-page__properties-text 
                        |Tripadvisor rating
                    .main-page__properties-col(data-aos='fade-up') 
                      .main-page__properties-img 
                        img.main-page__properties-image(src="assets/images/russia.png", alt="")
                      .main-page__properties-text 
                        |Unified Federal Register of Tour Operators
                    .main-page__properties-col(data-aos='fade-up') 
                      .main-page__properties-img 
                        +properties-3-svg
                      .main-page__properties-text 
                        |We always get back to the ship on time
  .modals 
    +team-modal(id='1')